Class ArrayBag<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • datastructures.other.ArrayBag<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bag<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>

    public class ArrayBag<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Bag<T>
    ArrayBag is a Bag based on a static array which is resized as required to fit more elements.
